  <brief_title>Long-Term Efficacy in AMD of Rheopheresis in North America</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Open Label, Prospective Study to Determine Safety and Efficacy Over an Additional 12-Month Period With Non-Exudative Age-Related Macular Degeneration (With Follow-on to 12-Months)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
