  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The primary objective of this study is to evaluate the change from baseline and ETDRS visual acuity in subjects with non-exudative AMD who participated in AMD-02-99.</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>The secondary objective of this study is to evaluate the safety of rheopheresis filtration treatments in subjects with non-exudative AMD as measured by AE's early DC's and Lab evaluations.</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
